name: Centroida OSS
body:
### Centroida's Open-source Software projects
 As a software company that strives to work with the latest technologies, we rely heavily on the open-source contributions. Because open-source has benefitted our organization's processes greatly, we are doing our best to improve the tools we already use and  publish our very own contributions.
